 have all heard the phrase, \\\"Where there is a will, there is a way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use it to motivate people to do hard things or to explain how someone did that hard thing, but there is a darker side to the phrase, too.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"hard things\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"that hard thing\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"a darker side\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where there is a will to do evil, there is a way.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany's extensive gun control laws could not prevent this and Georgia's relative lack of gun control laws did not cause Winder to happen.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2111, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9998780775102531, \"rank\": 5.022004674330972e-05, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Province_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9087394460367182, \"rank\": 0.09592966086393911, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Province_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Province_of_Georgia\"}, {\"begin\": 2233, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"ht