, \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wielder\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It simply is, and when placed in the hands of the good guys, it can stop evil.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"the good guys\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would seem to be a no-brainer to make sure more good guys have guns, then.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a no-brainer\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"more good guys\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"guns\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, that's not what happens.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Too many people see a no-brainer as a non-starter.\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Too many people\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-brainer\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They oppose it with every fiber of their being and there are enough of them, particularly in the media that likes to push an anti-gun narrative, for anything to change.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every fiber\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"an anti-gun narrative\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we will see terrorism and mass murders and know that the only thing anyone wants to do is the one thing we have seen fail time and time again.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terrorism and mass murders\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"the only th